-- SG CEO say Europe, Russia have common interest in Ukraine solution 
-- By Jeffrey Hodgson
-- Thu Dec 18, 2014 01:41PM EST
-- None



TORONTO, Dec 18 (Reuters) - Europe, Russia and the Ukraine have a common interest in finding a solution to the region's recent problems and Russia should be viewed as part of Europe, the chief executive of Societe Generale <SOGN.PA> said on Thursday.

"Just keep in mind that Russia is part of Europe," he told a business audience in Toronto. "From a political point of view and from an economic point of view, really ... Europe, Ukraine, Russia have a common interest to find a solution."